						<p><hi rend="bold">Vīra-Kampaṇa-uḍaiyār [Kali] 447., Śaka 12[9*]3, Virodhikṛit, Mithuna ba. 5, Wednesday, Aviṭṭam = 1371 A.D., June 4</hi><note n="520-1">Cf. A.R.Ep., 1914, p. 67, L.D.S. Pillai has equated the details of date to 4th May. But he also says that the record gives Dhanus as the month. While giving the Śaka year the writer of the record had skipped <ta>toṇṇūṟṟu</ta> in line 7.</note></p>						

